{"data": [{"id": "4741923", "title": "Microvast Holdings: Sell The Rally On Persistent Funding Needs", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1570041396/image_1570041396.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Lithium-ion High-voltage Battery Component for Electric Vehicle or Hybrid Car. Battery Module for Automotive Industry on Production Line. High Capacity Battery on Conveyor.\" data-id=\"1570041396\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1570041396/image_1570041396.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1570041396/image_1570041396.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1570041396/image_1570041396.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1570041396/image_1570041396.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1570041396/image_1570041396.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1570041396/image_1570041396.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1570041396/image_1570041396.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1570041396/image_1570041396.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">SweetBunFactory</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Similar to the majority of backdoor IPOs, lithium-ion battery manufacturer Microvast Holdings Inc. or \"Microvast\" (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MVST\" title=\"Microvast Holdings, Inc.\">MVST</a></span>, <span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MVSTW\" title=\"Microvast Holdings, Inc. WT EXP 040126\">MVSTW</a></span>) <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1760689/000121390021007125/ea134382ex99-1_tuscanhold.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1760689/000121390021007125/ea134382ex99-1_tuscanhold.htm\" target=\"_blank\">communicated</a> highly optimistic projections to the investment community when the company <a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1760689/000121390021038585/ea144763ex99-1_microvasthold.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1760689/000121390021038585/ea144763ex99-1_microvasthold.htm\" target=\"_blank\">listed</a> on Nasdaq in 2021:</p> <p>Unfortunately, things haven't gone according to plan:</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1570041396/image_1570041396.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741923-microvast-holdings-stock-sell-rally-persistent-funding-needs", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 06:02:10"}, {"id": "4741927", "title": "Thornburg Small/Mid Cap Growth Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367307622/image_1367307622.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Watering plant on money stack\" data-id=\"1367307622\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367307622/image_1367307622.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367307622/image_1367307622.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1367307622/image_1367307622.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.