alpha.com/article/4741927-thornburg-smallmid-cap-growth-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 05:35:00"}, {"id": "4741921", "title": "Archer-Daniels-Midland: Valuation Is Low, But Bunge May Be A Better Deal", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392050443/image_1392050443.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"ADM office building at their facility in Decatur, Illinois, USA.\" data-id=\"1392050443\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392050443/image_1392050443.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392050443/image_1392050443.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392050443/image_1392050443.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392050443/image_1392050443.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392050443/image_1392050443.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392050443/image_1392050443.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392050443/image_1392050443.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392050443/image_1392050443.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Last year, I covered the agricultural commodity giant Archer-Daniels-Midland (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ADM\" title=\"Archer-Daniels-Midland Company\">ADM</a></span>) in \"<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4616913-archer-daniels-midland-the-global-food-supply-chain-may-remain-tumultuous\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4616913-archer-daniels-midland-the-global-food-supply-chain-may-remain-tumultuous\" target=\"_blank\">Archer-Daniels-Midland: The Global Food Supply Chain May Remain Tumultuous.</a>\" My outlook was neutral, seeing that although its valuation was low and could grow long-term, it faced notable</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1392050443/image_1392050443.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741921-archer-daniels-midland-valuation-low-bunge-may-be-better-deal", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 05:29:58"}, {"id": "4741924", "title": "Thornburg International Growth Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334590383/image_1334590383.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Plant and graph chart growing with shape of arrow, Business investment and financial, Stock, Business growth, profit, development and success on nature background.\" data-id=\"1334590383\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334590383/image_1334590383.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334590383/image_1334590383.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334590383/image_1334590383.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334590383/image_1334590383.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334590383/image_1334590383.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334590383/image_1334590383.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334590383/image_1334590383.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334590383/image_1334590383.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">ipopba</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p></p> <p><strong>AVERAGE ANNUAL TOTAL RETURNS (%) AS OF 30 SEPTEMBER 2024</strong></p> <p></p> <span class=\"table-responsive\"><span class=\"table-scroll-wrapper\"><span data-intersection-boundary=\"start\"></span><table><tbody> <tr> <td></td> <td><p>QTR</p></td> <td><p>YTD</p></td> <td><p>1-YR</p></td> <td><p>3-YR</p></td> <td><p>5-YR</p></td> <td><p>10-YR</p></td> <td><p>ITD</p></td> </tr> <tr> <td><p>A Shares <span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">MUTF:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TIGAX\" title=\"Thornburg International Growth Fund A\">TIGAX</a></span> (Incep: 1 Feb 07)</p></td> <td></td> <td></td> <td></td> <td></td> <td></td> <td></td> <td></td> </tr> <tr> <td><p>Without sales charge</p></td> <td><p>1.92</p></td> <td><p>12.22</p></td> <td><p>25.81</p></td> <td><p>-1.32</p></td> <td><p>6.65</p></td> <td><p>5.80</p></td> <td><p>6.48</p></td> </tr> <tr> <td><p>With</p></td> </tr> </tbody></table> </span></span>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1334590383/image_1334590383.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741924-thornburg-international-growth-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 05:25:00"}, {"id": "4741919", "title": "LRT Capital Management November 2024 Investor Update", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912513618/image_1912513618.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Trade technology, and investment analysis.Business development, financial plan and strategy.Analysis finance graph and market chart investment\" data-id=\"1912513618\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1150px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912513618/image_1912513618.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912513618/image_1912513618.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912513618/image_1912513618.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912513618/image_1912513618.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912513618/image_1912513618.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912513618/image_1912513618.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912513618/image_1912513618.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912513618/image_1912513618.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Galeanu Mihai/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div></p> <h2>Dear Friends &amp; Partners,</h2> <p>Our investment returns are summarized in the table below:</p> <span class=\"table-responsive\"><span class=\"table-scroll-wrapper\"><span data-intersection-boundary=\"start\"></span><table><tbody> <tr> <td><p><strong>Strategy</strong></p></td> <td><p><strong>Month</strong></p></td> <td><p><strong>YTD</strong></p></td> <td><p><strong>12 Months</strong></p></td> <td><p><strong>24 Months</strong></p></td> <td><p><strong>36 Months</strong></p></td> <td><p><strong>Inception</strong></p></td> </tr> <tr> <td><p>LRT Global Opportunities</p></td> <td><p>+3.27%</p></td> <td><p>+24.78%</p></td> <td><p>+18.21%</p></td> <td><p>+11.72%</p></td> <td><p>-0.53%</p></td> <td><p>+19.55%</p></td> </tr> </tbody></table>\n<span data-intersection-boundary=\"end\"></span></span><button class=\"table-enlarge-button\"><svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"table-enlarge-icon\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16 11a5 5 0 0 1-5 5H5a5 5 0 0 1-5-5V5a5 5 0 0 1 5-5h6a5 5 0 0 1 5 5v6zm-4.5-2.5h2v-6h-6v2h4v4zm-9-1h2v4h4v2h-6v-6z\"></path></svg>Click to enlarge</button></span> <span class=\"table-responsive\"><span class=\"table-scroll-wrapper\"><span data-intersection-boundary=\"start\"></span><table><tbody><tr><td> Results as of 11/30/2024. Periods longer than one year are annualized. All results are net of all fees and expenses. Past returns are no guarantee of future results. Please see the end of this letter for additional disclosures. </td></tr></tbody></table>\n<span data-intersection-boundary=\"end\"></span></span><button class=\"table-enlarge-button\"><svg viewbox=\"0 0 16 16\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"table-enlarge-icon\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M16 11a5 5 0 0 1-5 5H5a5 5 0 0 1-5-5V5a5 5 0 0 1 5-5h6a5 5 0 0 1 5 5v6zm-4.5-2.5h2v-6h-6v2h4v4zm-9-1h2v4h4v2h-6v-6z\"></path></svg>Click to enlarge</button></span> <p>LRT Global Opportunities is a <strong>systematic</strong> long/ short strategy that seeks to generate positive returns while <strong>controlling downside risks</strong> and maintaining a low net exposure to the equity markets.</p> <p>For the month of November, the strategy was up<strong>+3.27%,</strong> bringing overall results to<strong>+24.78% for the year</strong>. All results are net of fees. Beta-adjusted net exposure was 23.42% as of December 2<sup>nd</sup><span>. The attribution of September\u2019s return was +1.34% from market beta, and +1.93% from our alpha generation.</span><sup>1</sup><span> Our longs contributed strongly to performance while our shorts detracted strongly. Top gainers on the long side included Comfort Systems USA Inc. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FIX\" title=\"Comfort Systems USA, Inc.\">FIX</a>), RLI Corp. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RLI\" title=\"RLI Corp.\">RLI</a>), Asbury Automotive Group, Inc. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ABG\" title=\"Asbury Automotive Group, Inc.\">ABG</a>), Apollo Global Management, LLC (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/APO\" title=\"Apollo Global Management, Inc.\">APO</a>) and Global Payments Inc. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GPN\" title=\"Global Payments Inc.\">GPN</a>) partially offset by losses on Booz Allen Hamilton Holding Corporation (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BAH\" title=\"Booz Allen Hamilton Holding Corporation\">BAH</a>), The Ensign Group, Inc. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ENSG\" title=\"The Ensign Group, Inc.\">ENSG</a>) and MarketAxess Holdings Inc. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MKTX\" title=\"MarketAxess Holdings Inc.\">MKTX</a>) See the appendix for additional disclosures.</span></p> <p>I take seriously the responsibility and the trust that you have given me as a steward of a part of your savings. As always, if you have any questions, please don\u2019t hesitate to contact me. I appreciate all your ongoing support.</p> <p><strong>Lukasz Tomicki | Portfolio Manager LRT Capital</strong></p> <p></p> <hr> <p>1Numbers may not add up due to rounding.</p> <p><strong>Attributions and Holdings as of 12/2/2024</strong></p> <span class=\"table-responsive\"><span class=\"table-scroll-wrapper\"><span data-intersection-boundary=\"start\"></span><table><tbody> <tr><td colspan=\"2\"><p><strong><em>Top Twenty Holdings (%) \u2013 As of 12/2/2024</em></strong></p></td></tr> <tr> <td><p>Ex